OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA damp morning with outbreaks
OL,6,Fof rain clearing eastwards. Turning
OL,7,Fdrier through the afternoon with a few
OL,8,Fshowers mixed with sunny spells later.
OL,9,FSomewhat less mild and fresher but
OL,10,Fwinds generally light.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FDry this evening with cloud
OL,13,Fbuilding overnight. Becoming wet and
OL,14,Fwindy by dawn with outbreaks of rain
OL,15,Fmoving in from the west. Generally a
OL,16,Flittle milder.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
