OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FCloudy with outbreaks of rain
OL,6,Fand drizzle, most persistent through
OL,7,Fthe morning with drier interludes
OL,8,Fduring the afternoon. Breezy and
OL,9,Fmilder.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:
OL,12,FFurther spells of rain on Monday in
OL,13,Fthe west with lighter winds. Drier
OL,14,Foverall on Tuesday and Wednesday with
OL,15,Fhigher pressure in charge. Staying
OL,16,Fmild with winds easing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
